     H            Y.
      ** AJPR02 **************************
      * CALCULATE DATE                   *
      *         TCH           07/22/04   *
      *
     F************************** AJPR02 **
     FAGDPL12 IF  E           K        DISK
      *------------------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1   8 WDATE
     I                                        1   2 @@YY
     I I            '.'                       3   3 W1
     I                                        4   5 @@MM
     I I            '.'                       6   6 W2
     I                                        7   8 @@DD
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@DAY   30
     C                     PARM           P@DAT   8
     C           K#AGD     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@YY    40
     C                     KFLD           K@MM    20
     C                     KFLD           K@DD    20
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*YEAR     K@YY
     C                     Z-ADD*MONTH    K@MM
     C                     Z-ADD*DAY      K@DD
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     @@CNT   30
     C           K#AGD     SETGTAGDPL12
     C           *IN90     DOUEQ*ON
     C                     READPAGDPL12                  90
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     ADD  1         @@CNT
     C           @@CNT     IFGE P@DAY
     C                     MOVE F8KAYY    @@YY    2
     C                     MOVE F8KAMM    @@MM    2
     C                     MOVE F8KADD    @@DD    2
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVE WDATE     P@DAT
      *
     C           @END      TAG
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
